#. <section class="sutta" id="an4.27"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an4.27:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 4"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 4"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.27:0.2"
msgid "3. Uruvelavagga"
msgstr "3. At Uruvelā"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an4.27:0.3"
msgid "27. Santuṭṭhisutta"
msgstr "27. Contentment"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pli2.27"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
#. VAR: ca → ceva (mr)
msgctxt "an4.27:1.1"
msgid "“Cattārimāni, bhikkhave, appāni ca sulabhāni ca, tāni ca anavajjāni."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, these four trifles are easy to get hold of and are blameless."

msgctxt "an4.27:1.2"
msgid "Katamāni cattāri?"
msgstr "What four?"

msgctxt "an4.27:1.3"
msgid "Paṃsukūlaṃ, bhikkhave, cīvarānaṃ appañca sulabhañca, tañca anavajjaṃ."
msgstr "Rag-robes …"

msgctxt "an4.27:1.4"
msgid "Piṇḍiyālopo, bhikkhave, bhojanānaṃ appañca sulabhañca, tañca anavajjaṃ."
msgstr "A lump of alms-food …"

msgctxt "an4.27:1.5"
msgid ""
"Rukkhamūlaṃ, bhikkhave, senāsanānaṃ appañca sulabhañca, tañca anavajjaṃ."
msgstr "Lodgings at the root of a tree …"

msgctxt "an4.27:1.6"
msgid "Pūtimuttaṃ, bhikkhave, bhesajjānaṃ appañca sulabhañca, tañca anavajjaṃ."
msgstr "Fermented urine as medicine …"

msgctxt "an4.27:1.7"
msgid ""
"Imāni kho, bhikkhave, cattāri appāni ca sulabhāni ca, tāni ca anavajjāni."
msgstr "These four trifles are easy to get hold of and are blameless."

#. VAR: sāmaññaṅganti → sāmaññanti (mr)
msgctxt "an4.27:1.8"
msgid ""
"Yato kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu appena ca tuṭṭho hoti sulabhena ca, idamassāhaṃ "
"aññataraṃ sāmaññaṅganti vadāmīti."
msgstr ""
"When a mendicant is content with trifles that are easy to get hold of, they "
"have one of the factors of the ascetic life, I say."

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an4.27:2.1"
msgid "Anavajjena tuṭṭhassa,"
msgstr "When you’re content with what’s blameless,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.27:2.2"
msgid "appena sulabhena ca;"
msgstr "trifling, and easy to get hold of,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.27:2.3"
msgid "Na senāsanamārabbha,"
msgstr "you don’t get upset"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.27:2.4"
msgid "cīvaraṃ pānabhojanaṃ;"
msgstr "about lodgings, robes,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.27:2.5"
msgid "Vighāto hoti cittassa,"
msgstr "food, and drink,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.27:2.6"
msgid "disā nappaṭihaññati."
msgstr "and you’re not obstructed anywhere."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an4.27:3.1"
msgid "Ye cassa dhammā akkhātā,"
msgstr "These qualities are said to be"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.27:3.2"
msgid "sāmaññassānulomikā;"
msgstr "integral to the ascetic life."

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.27:3.3"
msgid "Adhiggahitā tuṭṭhassa,"
msgstr "They’re acquired by one who trains,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.27:3.4"
msgid "appamattassa sikkhato”ti."
msgstr "content and diligent.”"

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.27:3.5"
msgid "Sattamaṃ."
msgstr ""
